		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>You hurl a hastily enchanted projectile from your sling.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Encounter</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Free Action</b><b> &#8226; </b>Personal</p><p><b>Effect:</b> You load your sling with a random type of ammunition. The next time you hit with a ranged basic attack with this sling before the end of your next turn, it has one of the following additional effects. Roll a d6 to determine the ammunition type. </p><p>1-2 Stinkpot: The target takes a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of its next turn. </p><p>3-4 Firepot (Fire): The target takes ongoing 2 fire damage (save ends). </p><p>5-6 Gluepot: The target is immobilized until the end of its next turn. </p><p>Published in Into the Unknown: The Dungeon Survival Handbook, page(s) 45. </p>",
